doc.title: Chidule cha Link Open With extension
doc.description:
Kuwonjezeraku kumakupatsani mwayi wowongolera momwe ma hyperlink amatsegukira mosavuta.

Zenera: asakatuli ena, mawindo owonekera, mazenera atsopano, mazenera a incognito, zenera lapano (lofikira)

Machubu: kumanzere kwa tabu yamakono, tsamba lapano, kumanja kwa tsamba lapano (losasintha)

Mkhalidwe wotsegula: wasiya, yambitsani nthawi yomweyo (zofikira)
